{"tid":821290,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳侵仔已落實向2000億美元中國貨收10%關稅，最快星期一公布","createTime":"2018-09-16T01:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T12:27:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7961515a95c9e79e645c43ba230874f7760e687b","tid":821290,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:57:31.000Z","msg":"President Donald Trump is readying a fresh round of tariffs on Chinese goods ahead of scheduled trade talks with Beijing, The Wall Street Journal reported on Saturday, which is expected to affect $200 billion worth of goods.<br />\n<br />\nThe Journal's report dovetailed with a report from Bloomberg on Friday, in which the president is said to have directed his aides to proceed with plans to hit China's imports again &mdash; even as both sides prepare to meet in order to dial back on trade tensions. The new tariffs will be set at 10 percent, sources familiar with the matter told The Journal, below an original figure of 25 percent floated by the administration earlier.....<br />\n<br />\nThe president is also expected to threaten to hike tariffs again to squeeze Beijing at the negotiating table, the report noted.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/09/15/trump-set-to-slap-200-billion-in-tariffs-on-chinese-goods-wsj.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2Ftrump-set-to-slap-200-billion-in-tariffs-on-chinese-goods-wsj.html&d=IvkgohKqJAFGbusf%2FYGjTy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5eff8b60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2018/09/15/trump-set-to-slap-200-billion-in-tariffs-on-chinese-goods-wsj.html</a><br />\n<br />\nDonald Trump to impose tariffs on US$200 billion in Chinese goods as early as Monday<br />\n<br />\nThe new tariffs at 10 per cent would apply to more than 1,000 products, likely leading to higher prices for US consumers<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.scmp.com/news/china/article/2164394/donald-trump-has-reportedly-decided-go-ahead-tariffs-us200-billion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2164394%2Fdonald-trump-has-reportedly-decided-go-ahead-tariffs-us200-billion&d=IvkgohKqJAFGbusf%2FYGjTy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=906cc937\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.scmp.com/news/china/article/2164394/donald-trump-has-reportedly-decided-go-ahead-tariffs-us200-billion</a>"},{"pid":"fb176508afbf611ad91b73870018a458cc9b4486","tid":821290,"uid":32577,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:59:37.000Z","msg":"慘啦，香港政府實帶頭話hk is not china"},{"pid":"06c87595c94987a5c1e431bac343fb31b15b5661","tid":821290,"uid":16925,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:02:32.000Z","msg":"條友次次談判之前都會講狗話"},{"pid":"c3f64a4ab01c0c4a726d09663b0267d7737c200a","tid":821290,"uid":40428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083c7b0fcc7b4402eb33062b008568de92571648","tid":821290,"uid":147097,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8f5b1c7c43c6d20b549a8f36dffb1de9afc6bc","tid":821290,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"083c7b0fcc7b4402eb33062b008568de92571648","tid":821290,"uid":147097,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c3d1d4372ab808a68b2c009e4e3b3a0b41a17d","tid":821290,"uid":147097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed8f5b1c7c43c6d20b549a8f36dffb1de9afc6bc","tid":821290,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"083c7b0fcc7b4402eb33062b00